articles.title: Carolina Wilga, German woman who went missing in Australia's remote Outback, found alive after 12 days - CBS News
articles.description: Carolina Wilga was found alive in Australia's remote Outback 12 days after she went missing and a day after her abandoned van was spotted by a helicopter crew.
